The kitchen is equipped with updated countertops, tile backsplash, ample cabinets, a breakfast bar, and breakfast nook. Entertaining is a breeze with this great floor plan complete with cozy fireplace. Relax in your primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. Relax with your favorite drink in the fenced in backyard with a patio, lush grass, and great potential for adding personal touches. Don't wait! Make this beautiful home yours today.

This home has been virtually Staged to show its potential.
